\textbf{Frequency band structure -}

The dispersion relation for the Bloch index $\mu_B$ determined through the eigenvalues $\exp(\pm i\mu_B)$ of the transfer $\hat{M}$-matrix, is defined by the matrix trace, $2\cos\mu_B=M_{11}+M_{22}$. Thus, one obtains

